    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: February 2026</p>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        By accessing and using Program Car Remotes, you accept and agree to be bound by these 
        Terms of Use. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the site.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Use of Content</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        The content on this site is for personal, non-commercial use only. You may:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="text-gray-700">View, download, and print pages for your own use</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
          </svg>
          <span class="text-gray-700">Share links to our pages</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
        You may <strong class="text-gray-900">not</strong> republish, sell, or redistribute our content without permission.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-8 mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">ℹ️ Accuracy of Information</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        We strive to keep our programming instructions accurate and up-to-date. However, vehicle 
        manufacturers may change procedures. We recommend verifying procedures are current for 
        your specific vehicle before proceeding.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8 mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        Program Car Remotes and its owners shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, 
        incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the site or 
        reliance on any information provided.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Continued use of the site 
        constitutes acceptance of any changes.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Questions about these terms? <a href="/contact/" class="text-primary hover:underline font-medium">Contact us</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
